                     <interp inst="t18310630-43-person424" type="gender" value="female"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I was in John-street, leading to Brewer-street, on the 17th of June. I saw the prisoner take a yellow silk handkerchief from a gentleman's pocket who was walking along - it was such a one as has been produced.</p>
